  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Hakunetsu Pro Yakyuu '94 Ganba League 3 is the third and final Super Famicom baseball game from Sting Entertainment and Epic/Sony Records. Like its two predecessors, the game adopts a super-deformed cartoon style.\n\nHakunetsu Pro Yakyuu '94 Ganba League 3 follows Hakunetsu Pro Yakyuu Ganba League (best known in the US as Extra Innings) and Hakunetsu Pro Yakyuu Ganba League '93.",
